data.description: Major improvements made to this Designer remodel set-up for multi-generational living. New roof, 30x40 shop/garage, new wiring, siding, insulation, stainless-steel appliances, 4-season sun porch, large deck on front, privacy fence and MORE - SEE attached list. 1.85 acre gorgeous lot with mature trees, fruit trees, vegetable garden area. All on ONE level with attached in-law suite w/full kitchen, bath with walk-in shower, living room & deck. Granite counters with solid cherry shaker cabinets in main house. Energy efficient windows throughout. Gated security entrance. Gorgeous hardwood floors. Move in ready! A must see to appreciate.
